name: SuperLite Gold Series: Minna no Shougi: Shokyuu Hen
overview: SuperLite Gold Series - Minna no Shougi - Shokyuu Hen (Beginner's class) is a shogi game designed specially for beginners. The game features different difficulty levels from beginner to strongest, 3 different kind of boards, pieces & cursors.
